  <h2>What is Deal Drops?</h2>
  <p>Deal Drops is a <strong>deals and coupons website for India</strong>. We find the best offers on Amazon, Flipkart, Myntra, Swiggy, and other popular stores — and share them with you before they expire.</p>
  <p>No fake countdown timers. No expired codes. No clickbait. Just real deals that actually work.</p>

  <h2>How We Verify Deals</h2>
  <p>Every deal on this site goes through a simple but strict process before it goes live:</p>
  <ul style="list-style:disc;padding-left:1.5rem;color:var(--text-muted);font-size:0.93rem;line-height:1.9;margin-bottom:0.75rem;">
    <li>We check the price directly on the store's website</li>
    <li>We personally test any coupon codes</li>
    <li>We verify the deal is available in India</li>
    <li>We add expiry dates where known</li>
    <li>We remove or mark deals as expired once they're no longer valid</li>
  </ul>
  <p>If you ever find a deal that's expired or has an incorrect price, let us know on <a href="{{ site.instagram }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener" style="color:var(--accent);font-weight:600;">Instagram</a> and we'll fix it right away.</p>

  <h2>The Team</h2>
  <p>Deal Drops is run by a small team that genuinely loves finding good deals. We started this project because we were tired of "deal" sites that post hundreds of links without checking if they even work.</p>
  <p>We'd rather share 5 verified deals a day than 50 broken ones.</p>

